flowchart LR
  subgraph Inputs
    TROP[TROPOMI — NO2/HCHO/O3/CO/SO2]
    INS[INSAT-3D — AOD]
    ERA[ERA5 — T/RH/U10/V10/BLH/TP]
    FIR[FIRMS — fire_count]
    CPC[CPCB — ground PM2.5]
  end

  TROP --> Preproc[Preprocessing & Grid Aggregation: build_dataset_aqi.py / build_dataset_hcho.py]
  INS --> Preproc
  ERA --> Preproc
  FIR --> Preproc
  CPC --> Preproc

  Preproc --> Seq[Sequence Builder: sliding window of T days per cell]
  Seq --> Conv[Spatial Encoder: Time-distributed Conv layers / shared CNN]
  Conv --> TD[Time-distributed Features: Flatten/pooling per timestep]
  TD --> LSTM[LSTM/GRU: temporal fusion across T timesteps]
  LSTM --> Dense[Fully-connected layers]
  Dense --> PM25[PM2.5 Prediction]
  PM25 --> AQI[AQI Conversion & Postprocessing]
  AQI --> Output[Gridded AQI map / per-cell predictions]

  subgraph ModelArtifacts
    CKPT[Model checkpoint — .pt / .ckpt]
    METR[Metrics & eval reports]
  end

  Dense --> CKPT
  Dense --> METR
